<h1>Praize Support</h1>
<p>Praize helps you identify secondhand items and estimate their resale value.</p>

<h2>Contact us</h2>
<p>Questions, bug reports, or subscription help? Email
<a href="mailto:downloadpraize@gmail.com">downloadpraize@gmail.com</a> and we'll get back to you.</p>

<h2>Common questions</h2>
<ul>
  <li><strong>How do I scan an item?</strong> Open the Scan tab, point your camera at an item, and tap the shutter. Add a close-up of the tag or label for the best match.</li>
  <li><strong>Free scans &amp; Premium:</strong> You get 5 free scans. Praize Premium unlocks unlimited scanning with a 1-week free trial, then $9.99/month. Manage or cancel anytime in your App Store account settings.</li>
  <li><strong>Delete your data:</strong> Profile → Delete Account permanently removes your account, saved scans, and stored photos.</li>
</ul>

